             were indicted for <rs id="t18210411-147-off900" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18210411-147-off900" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210411-147-off900" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18210411-147-cd901" type="crimeDate">11th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210411-147-off900 t18210411-147-cd901"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210411-147-off902 t18210411-147-cd901"></join>, four coach glasses, value 3 l.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18210411-147-victim1507" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Jones
                  <interp inst="t18210411-147-victim1507" type="surname" value="Jones"></interp>
