            </rs>.</p>
               <p>LEDDINGHAM - <rs id="t18210411-147-verdict908" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18210411-147-verdict908" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
